<h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">AAAI-13 Invited Speakers</span></h2>


<p>
AAAI-13 will feature the following series of distinguished speakers:
</p>

<ul>
<li>AAAI Keynote Address<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Mooney">Raymond Mooney</a> (University of Texas at Austin)</li>

<li>AAAI 2013 Robert S. Engelmore Lecture Award<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#McGuinness">Deborah L. McGuinness</a> (Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute)</li>

<li>AAAI-13 Invited Talks<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Bennett">Kristin P. Bennett</a> (Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute)<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Kumar">Vijay Kumar</a> (University of Pennsylvania)<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Mataric">Maja Mataric</a> (University of Southern California)<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Sandholm">Tuomas Sandholm</a> (Carnegie Mellon University)</li>

<li>Joint AAAI/IAAI Invited Talk<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Birnbaum">Larry Birnbaum</a> (Northwestern University)</li>

<li>IAAI-13 Invited Talk<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Hunter">Lawrence Hunter</a> (University of Colorado)</li>
