<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Rychtyckyj">Nestor Rychtyckyj and Howie (Hao) Yang </a> (Ford Motor Company)</li>



<li>EAAI-13 Invited Talk<br >
<a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI/2013/aaai13speakers.php#Klein">Dan Klein</a> (University of California, Berkeley)</li>
<li>EAAI-13 Invited Talk<br >
